WEBVTT

01:43.090 --> 01:46.039
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.100 --> 01:49.039
[Episode 6]

01:49.110 --> 01:52.580
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

02:13.070 --> 02:13.740
Dr. Lu.

02:18.390 --> 02:20.640
[Medical expertise conquers intractable diseases
Medical ethics spread across borders]

02:20.710 --> 02:23.760
[Exemplary in both ethics and expertise, with compassion for patients]

02:25.160 --> 02:25.860
What's up?

02:28.100 --> 02:28.810
Are you alright?

02:30.530 --> 02:31.110
What's up?

02:32.120 --> 02:33.740
You cooperated with the bomb disposal,

02:33.770 --> 02:34.590
and

02:35.010 --> 02:36.810
did my dad's surgery this time.

02:37.070 --> 02:37.730
I want to...

02:38.440 --> 02:39.130
Express my gratitude.

02:41.630 --> 02:43.810
W-We can't accept gifts.

02:43.829 --> 02:44.700
We have discipline,

02:44.700 --> 02:45.510
like you do.

02:48.010 --> 02:48.440
Well...

02:48.900 --> 02:50.110
Not even a silk banner?

02:50.880 --> 02:51.570
Silk banner?

02:52.980 --> 02:54.630
Oh, it's a silk banner?

02:54.790 --> 02:55.620
We can accept silk banners.

02:55.670 --> 02:56.650
We've got many here.

02:57.350 --> 02:58.630
Did you get the credits right?

02:58.710 --> 02:59.790
The credit should go to Dr. Han

02:59.829 --> 03:01.810
and all medical staff.

03:01.960 --> 03:02.900
We need to include that many people?

03:03.620 --> 03:04.760
Yes. The credit goes to all of them, right?

03:05.640 --> 03:06.880
What if

03:07.220 --> 03:08.630
I want to give a special thanks to you?

03:09.990 --> 03:11.760
You want to give me a special thanks?

03:13.700 --> 03:15.370
If you want to give me a special thanks...

03:17.270 --> 03:18.190
Well,

03:19.329 --> 03:21.050
write me a letter of commendation then.

03:21.500 --> 03:22.890
A letter of commendation just for you,

03:22.920 --> 03:23.650
right?

03:26.370 --> 03:27.920
I thought you were

03:27.990 --> 03:28.790
not interested in fame nor wealth.

03:28.810 --> 03:29.710
I didn't expect you

03:29.730 --> 03:30.790
wanting to be singled out for praise.

03:30.910 --> 03:32.300
You don't have to write it.

03:32.350 --> 03:33.690
You said it yourself that

03:33.720 --> 03:34.840
you wanted to give me a special thanks.

03:39.790 --> 03:40.840
[Letter of Commendation]

03:44.180 --> 03:45.570
Specially to praise you.

03:47.070 --> 03:49.130
[Letter of Commendation]

03:53.000 --> 03:53.970
Dr. Lu.

03:56.210 --> 03:57.260
Are you free

03:59.050 --> 03:59.920
tonight?

04:01.450 --> 04:03.410
I... Tonight...

04:08.580 --> 04:09.260
Okay.

04:09.500 --> 04:10.030
I'll be right there.

04:10.070 --> 04:10.680
Go ahead.

04:11.230 --> 04:11.860
Excuse me.

04:26.270 --> 04:26.950
Dad.

04:26.980 --> 04:27.630
Mom.

04:28.180 --> 04:28.790
What do you want to eat?

04:28.810 --> 04:29.530
I'll go get us food from the canteen.

04:29.830 --> 04:30.740
Braised pork.

04:30.920 --> 04:31.710
No meat allowed.

04:32.780 --> 04:33.800
Keep eating porridge.

04:35.540 --> 04:36.300
Get an extra portion.

04:36.350 --> 04:37.320
Jing will be here later.

04:37.870 --> 04:38.560
Which Jing?

04:38.850 --> 04:40.700
Jing, Aunt Zhang's daughter.

04:40.990 --> 04:42.340
She just came back from abroad.

04:42.430 --> 04:43.760
She heard that your dad had an operation,

04:43.790 --> 04:44.630
so she wanted to come and visit him.

04:44.650 --> 04:45.950
The one who used to

04:45.990 --> 04:47.690
come to our house a lot to play with our son?

04:47.909 --> 04:48.470
Yes.

04:48.510 --> 04:49.680
That ugly little girl.

04:49.710 --> 04:51.520
How can you call her ugly girl?

04:52.110 --> 04:52.630
Alright.

04:52.730 --> 04:53.390
I'll go then.

04:53.570 --> 04:54.310
Okay, go ahead.

04:55.659 --> 04:57.490
[Emergency Department]

04:59.680 --> 05:00.720
Thank you, Dr. Lu.

05:00.790 --> 05:01.350
You're welcome.

05:01.370 --> 05:02.170
Call me if you need anything.

05:02.240 --> 05:02.750
Okay.

05:08.510 --> 05:09.430
Dr. Lu.

05:11.640 --> 05:12.720
Are you free

05:14.580 --> 05:15.340
tonight?

05:16.280 --> 05:18.350
He wanted to ask me out for dinner.

05:18.390 --> 05:19.890
Should I go out with him?

05:22.270 --> 05:23.230
What's there to think about?

05:23.250 --> 05:24.070
We're just friends.

05:24.070 --> 05:25.110
What's wrong with having dinner with a friend?

05:25.430 --> 05:26.340
Besides,

05:26.670 --> 05:28.130
I'll have to eat anyway.

05:28.240 --> 05:29.630
What's the difference between eating with him

05:29.660 --> 05:30.800
and with others?

05:31.990 --> 05:33.570
If he asks me out again,

05:33.730 --> 05:34.570
I'll say yes.

05:45.400 --> 05:46.350
You've come up?

05:46.530 --> 05:47.780
Why are you here?

05:47.810 --> 05:48.860
Are you here to pick me up?

05:48.880 --> 05:50.130
My dad was worried you couldn't find the ward.

05:51.150 --> 05:51.630
This way.

05:51.650 --> 05:52.500
Uncle is so sweet.

05:53.520 --> 05:55.000
Look at you.

05:55.020 --> 05:55.640
You didn't even tell us

05:55.670 --> 05:56.830
Uncle was ill.

05:57.240 --> 05:58.070
I didn't want

05:58.090 --> 05:59.140
many people to know.

05:59.350 --> 06:00.230
You didn't have to tell others,

06:00.270 --> 06:00.750
but you should at least

06:00.750 --> 06:01.990
have told us.

06:02.840 --> 06:04.040
How is he recovering?

06:04.060 --> 06:04.730
He's feeling much better.

06:05.100 --> 06:05.870
That's good.

06:06.230 --> 06:07.690
So, do you have time

06:07.720 --> 06:09.020
to have dinner with me some time?

06:09.040 --> 06:10.590
I can't leave his side.

06:24.470 --> 06:25.190
Yan.

06:28.100 --> 06:28.700
Yan.

06:29.240 --> 06:30.990
What are you doing? You didn't respond.

06:32.150 --> 06:32.830
I...

06:33.820 --> 06:35.440
I'm... I'm just drinking water.

06:35.510 --> 06:36.720
Drinking water?

06:37.040 --> 06:38.680
You look preoccupied.

06:38.950 --> 06:39.630
Your expression just now

06:39.680 --> 06:40.550
was like my Shiba Inu

06:40.570 --> 06:41.730
when it did something wrong.

06:42.330 --> 06:43.680
Who are you calling a dog?

06:44.130 --> 06:45.430
So what were you thinking about?

06:45.780 --> 06:46.290
I...

06:47.620 --> 06:48.590
I wasn't thinking about anything.

06:48.610 --> 06:49.740
I'll go check on a patient.

06:50.230 --> 06:51.600
Yan, which patient?

06:53.230 --> 06:53.770
I...

06:53.940 --> 06:54.920
I'm going to...

06:56.909 --> 06:58.600
What does this have to do with you?

06:59.230 --> 07:00.790
Shouldn't you be observing the operation at 2 pm?

07:01.280 --> 07:02.050
I...

07:02.280 --> 07:03.280
I'll go right away.

07:12.400 --> 07:14.120
Jing, you've grown up.

07:14.160 --> 07:14.950
Yeah.

07:15.060 --> 07:15.710
Speaking of which,

07:15.750 --> 07:17.390
you actually watched me grow up.

07:17.540 --> 07:19.110
Jiang Chengyi and I

07:19.130 --> 07:20.380
often went to school together.

07:20.420 --> 07:22.050
You gave us a ride a few times, right?

07:23.560 --> 07:24.370
That's true.

07:24.400 --> 07:25.350
I remember

07:25.350 --> 07:26.230
you bullied him quite a lot when you were kids.

07:27.220 --> 07:28.810
I didn't.

07:29.110 --> 07:30.360
Dr. Lu.

07:31.140 --> 07:32.100
It's really you.

07:32.120 --> 07:33.270
Why are you here?

07:33.820 --> 07:35.280
I... I thought

07:35.310 --> 07:35.950
I'd come to check

07:35.970 --> 07:37.180
how Uncle's recovering.

07:37.730 --> 07:38.870
You are so responsible.

07:38.890 --> 07:40.170
Come on in.

07:41.430 --> 07:42.020
Jiang.

07:42.040 --> 07:43.730
Dr. Lu is here to see you.

07:44.200 --> 07:45.590
Hello, Dr. Lu.

07:45.860 --> 07:46.560
Lu Yan?

07:47.730 --> 07:48.740
Why are you here?

07:49.360 --> 07:50.710
She works here.

07:54.659 --> 07:56.100
You know each other?

07:56.270 --> 07:56.850
Yes.

07:56.880 --> 07:58.340
We went to the same university.

07:59.120 --> 07:59.550
You...

08:00.230 --> 08:00.880
University...

08:01.870 --> 08:02.670
So You and Chengyi

08:02.710 --> 08:03.870
should be fellow university alumni too.

08:03.990 --> 08:05.340
You don't know each other?

08:10.630 --> 08:11.380
Auntie.

08:11.410 --> 08:12.700
There were so many students in our university.

08:12.720 --> 08:14.090
How could they all know each other?

08:14.230 --> 08:15.520
Unlike Jiang Chengyi and me.

08:15.550 --> 08:17.140
We've been together since middle school.

08:17.400 --> 08:18.320
We should be considered

08:18.350 --> 08:19.600
childhood sweethearts, Uncle.

08:20.600 --> 08:21.970
How did you come to this conclusion?

08:21.990 --> 08:23.500
There are thousands of students in a school.

08:23.530 --> 08:25.320
Are they all childhood sweethearts?

08:25.830 --> 08:26.490
Why are you

08:26.510 --> 08:27.960
still so annoying?

08:27.990 --> 08:29.540
You've always been so mean.

08:30.510 --> 08:31.340
Uncle.

08:31.770 --> 08:32.799
Do you still have a headache?

08:33.679 --> 08:34.280
No.

08:34.299 --> 08:35.409
Thank you, Dr. Lu.

08:36.090 --> 08:37.169
Dr. Lu.

08:37.270 --> 08:38.940
He does feel much better,

08:39.070 --> 08:39.789
but

08:39.830 --> 08:41.370
I still feel uneasy.

08:41.950 --> 08:42.630
Can you let him

08:42.650 --> 08:43.929
stay in the hospital for a few more days?

08:44.350 --> 08:45.620
Auntie, don't worry.

08:45.700 --> 08:46.550
Patients have to be examined and evaluated

08:46.570 --> 08:47.440
before they are discharged.

08:47.470 --> 08:49.030
We can't just let patients leave the hospital rashly.

08:49.090 --> 08:50.190
Will you be the one doing the evaluation?

08:50.840 --> 08:52.400
There are specialized doctors for that.

08:53.110 --> 08:54.950
I want you to do it.

08:55.110 --> 08:56.350
This way, I can feel at ease.

08:56.820 --> 08:57.240
Okay.

08:57.270 --> 08:58.500
I'll come by when the time comes.

08:59.160 --> 09:00.780
That's good. Did you hear that?

09:02.650 --> 09:03.790
Thank you, Dr. Lu.

09:04.640 --> 09:05.080
Come on.

09:05.290 --> 09:06.690
Have some strawberries. I just washed them.

09:06.720 --> 09:07.480
No, no, no.

09:07.500 --> 09:08.130
Thank you, Auntie.

09:08.160 --> 09:09.080
Have some.

09:09.110 --> 09:10.020
Uncle.

09:10.040 --> 09:11.000
I have a favor

09:11.030 --> 09:11.830
to ask of you.

09:11.850 --> 09:12.650
Go ahead.

09:13.090 --> 09:14.240
Look.

09:14.510 --> 09:15.580
Chengyi and I

09:15.670 --> 09:17.220
haven't seen each other for such a long time.

09:17.570 --> 09:19.020
I want to borrow him from you for a bit

09:19.040 --> 09:20.080
so that we can have dinner together.

09:20.110 --> 09:21.210
No problem.

09:21.780 --> 09:22.560
Son.

09:22.880 --> 09:23.550
You haven't seen her for quite a while.

09:23.600 --> 09:24.830
Take Jing out for a walk,

09:24.870 --> 09:26.030
and find a nice place

09:26.050 --> 09:27.360
to have dinner and have a chat.

09:27.410 --> 09:28.390
Sure, in a few days.

09:28.390 --> 09:29.170
Tonight, I still

09:29.190 --> 09:30.370
have to...

09:30.650 --> 09:31.450
This...

09:31.480 --> 09:32.520
I don't need you young people

09:32.540 --> 09:33.460
to stay here with me.

09:33.500 --> 09:34.830
I actually feel uneasy with you here.

09:34.860 --> 09:36.020
I want to be alone for a while.

09:36.050 --> 09:37.030
Go now.

09:37.410 --> 09:38.320
Go. Go.

09:38.320 --> 09:39.370
Thank you, Uncle.

09:43.320 --> 09:44.570
I'll leave now.

09:44.750 --> 09:45.350
I still have work to do.

09:45.370 --> 09:46.610
Take the strawberries.

09:46.640 --> 09:47.480
No need.

09:57.710 --> 09:58.500
Lu Yan.

09:58.930 --> 09:59.560
Lu Yan.

09:59.580 --> 10:01.140
I have work to do. I have to go.

10:07.080 --> 10:07.670
Chengyi.

10:07.690 --> 10:08.520
What should we eat?

10:10.430 --> 10:11.230
Well,

10:11.390 --> 10:12.440
I really have something to do today.

10:12.540 --> 10:13.680
Let's do it next time.

10:15.010 --> 10:16.870
Didn't you promise Uncle?

10:18.580 --> 10:19.350
Ding Jing.

10:20.530 --> 10:22.110
I actually know what you mean.

10:22.470 --> 10:23.390
All these years,

10:23.410 --> 10:24.910
I've made it very clear to you.

10:25.400 --> 10:26.770
We are just classmates.

10:28.230 --> 10:28.800
Thank you

10:28.820 --> 10:29.960
for coming to visit my dad today.

10:30.190 --> 10:31.810
So you can't even give me a chance?

10:31.900 --> 10:33.390
Not even a meal?

10:33.410 --> 10:34.530
Listen to me.

10:34.880 --> 10:35.820
I really have

10:35.860 --> 10:37.320
an important person to meet today.

10:37.850 --> 10:38.460
Another time.

10:39.350 --> 10:40.220
Thank you.

10:52.210 --> 10:53.510
I think Jing is a good girl.

10:53.550 --> 10:55.120
The doctor said you can't smell this.

10:55.260 --> 10:57.130
Why did she bring flowers of all gifts?

10:58.110 --> 10:59.300
She's pretty

10:59.320 --> 11:00.510
and has a good personality.

11:00.960 --> 11:02.460
Our families

11:02.510 --> 11:03.510
have known each other for three generations.

11:03.540 --> 11:04.610
We know each other very well.

11:07.920 --> 11:08.680
Pretty good.

11:09.640 --> 11:11.630
If she's to be our daughter-in-law...

11:11.650 --> 11:12.350
Right?

11:15.520 --> 11:16.210
Hey.

11:16.950 --> 11:17.590
Didn't you ask me

11:17.610 --> 11:18.910
to take more vitamins?

11:19.490 --> 11:20.450
The doctor said you haven't fully recovered.

11:20.470 --> 11:21.330
You can't eat this.

11:24.510 --> 11:25.710
You're always right.

11:38.900 --> 11:40.040
Do you understand what's going on?

11:40.510 --> 11:42.170
Of course I do.

11:42.200 --> 11:42.870
Look.

11:42.920 --> 11:43.880
The forward is...

11:47.740 --> 11:48.520
I didn't wash them clean.

11:48.550 --> 11:49.240
I'll go wash them again.

11:55.060 --> 11:57.050
What do you think of Jing?

11:57.770 --> 11:59.370
You should be alone for a while.

12:13.920 --> 12:20.860
[Would you like to accompany me back to school for a walk? I'll wait for you at the hospital entrance. See you after work.]

12:41.670 --> 12:42.570
Are you off work?

12:42.840 --> 12:44.120
I was just passing by the hospital.

12:44.150 --> 12:45.150
Do you want to have dinner together?

12:48.700 --> 12:50.680
I have an appointment tonight.

12:50.710 --> 12:51.460
Maybe next time.

12:55.620 --> 12:57.250
Is it something very important?

12:57.570 --> 12:58.770
[Outpatient]

13:05.090 --> 13:06.340
Did you wait for long?

13:06.690 --> 13:07.350
No.

13:07.370 --> 13:08.080
Just a little while.

13:09.730 --> 13:10.220
Let's go.

13:10.400 --> 13:11.140
Get in.

13:51.520 --> 13:57.870
[Ninghai University]

14:07.570 --> 14:08.600
Wait, I can't.

14:08.630 --> 14:09.500
I can't run any longer.

14:10.770 --> 14:12.020
Can you hang in there for one more lap?

14:12.190 --> 14:12.950
If you do one more lap,

14:12.970 --> 14:14.310
I'll take you to eat something nice tonight.

14:14.430 --> 14:15.370
Are you serious?

14:15.430 --> 14:16.460
Of course.

14:16.630 --> 14:17.780
If you lie, you'll be a puppy.

14:25.700 --> 14:27.120
Keep your breathing rhythm steady.

14:28.270 --> 14:29.900
Let your thighs lead your calves when you run.

14:30.570 --> 14:31.480
Use your thighs.

14:31.510 --> 14:32.030
Like this?

14:32.050 --> 14:32.580
Yes.

14:32.840 --> 14:33.700
Let your thighs lead your calves.

14:52.760 --> 14:53.630
Do you remember?

14:54.230 --> 14:55.230
You were like this back then.

14:55.830 --> 14:56.950
You still remember?

14:57.510 --> 14:58.050
Yeah.

15:07.400 --> 15:09.260
Do you want to have

15:09.320 --> 15:10.180
spicy hot pot later?

15:10.200 --> 15:11.340
At the restaurant you like.

15:11.840 --> 15:12.630
Is it still open?

15:12.820 --> 15:13.520
It is.

15:14.330 --> 15:15.030
Sure.

15:23.960 --> 15:24.910
Do you remember this place?

15:25.910 --> 15:26.360
Definitely.

15:27.120 --> 15:28.350
Every time we went to and from school,

15:28.370 --> 15:29.640
we had to pass by here.

15:29.740 --> 15:30.460
Right.

15:31.960 --> 15:32.770
Back then,

15:33.630 --> 15:34.400
we even chased

15:34.430 --> 15:35.430
a thief here.

15:35.840 --> 15:39.250
[Soap]

15:36.780 --> 15:37.690
Indeed.

15:41.140 --> 15:42.070
It hasn't changed at all,

15:42.350 --> 15:43.330
after all these years.

15:44.010 --> 15:45.100
All these years.

15:45.270 --> 15:46.670
It still feels the same.

15:56.540 --> 15:57.750
It's still here. Look.

16:05.390 --> 16:06.450
It's this way, right?

16:06.930 --> 16:07.280
Right?

16:07.320 --> 16:07.680
Yes.

16:13.200 --> 16:15.110
Here's your spicy hot pot.

16:15.140 --> 16:15.690
Thank you.

16:16.040 --> 16:18.710
[Spicy Hot Pot]

16:16.770 --> 16:18.550
It's been a long time since I last saw you.

16:18.900 --> 16:20.380
You still remember us?

16:20.550 --> 16:21.940
I do!

16:22.130 --> 16:23.790
Your favorite is vermicelli noodles,

16:23.820 --> 16:25.630
and your favorite is meat, right?

16:25.660 --> 16:26.740
Yes. That's right.

16:27.600 --> 16:28.510
You know what?

16:28.650 --> 16:29.430
At that time,

16:29.470 --> 16:30.070
your boyfriend

16:30.110 --> 16:31.860
even added me on WeChat,

16:31.880 --> 16:34.040
and often asked me to save a portion for you.

16:39.710 --> 16:43.170
[Spicy Hot Pot]

16:40.110 --> 16:42.000
It's nice that you are still together.

16:42.430 --> 16:43.440
You must be married now, right?

16:43.630 --> 16:44.850
How old is your child?

16:45.630 --> 16:46.350
We...

16:46.350 --> 16:47.110
Well...

16:48.870 --> 16:50.200
Well, it's normal.

16:50.380 --> 16:51.700
Young people nowadays

16:51.730 --> 16:53.030
don't rush to have children anymore.

16:54.020 --> 16:55.500
Boss, one portion of oden please.

16:55.560 --> 16:56.330
Coming.

16:56.870 --> 16:58.190
Enjoy your meal. I'll get back to work.

16:58.230 --> 16:58.680
Go ahead.

16:58.710 --> 16:59.440
Let me know if you need anything.

16:59.440 --> 17:00.030
Okay.

17:05.950 --> 17:06.510
Let's eat.

17:11.210 --> 17:12.440
You can have my vermicelli noodles.

17:19.550 --> 17:20.349
Okay.

17:24.490 --> 17:25.859
Didn't I tell you

17:25.880 --> 17:26.800
the noodles would get soggy?

17:29.000 --> 17:30.220
They got soggy. Why are you still filming?

17:30.250 --> 17:30.870
See?

17:31.490 --> 17:32.750
You can't put so much in one bowl.

17:32.780 --> 17:33.710
I told you.

17:34.030 --> 17:34.990
What should we do now?

17:35.050 --> 17:35.980
Stop filming.

17:36.010 --> 17:36.990
I'll film you too.

17:38.190 --> 17:39.960
You're filming me? Then I'll eat your beef.

17:41.740 --> 17:43.460
I thought you didn't like vermicelli noodles.

17:43.630 --> 17:45.150
They're already soggy, so I'll eat them for you.

17:45.150 --> 17:46.100
You eat the vegetables.

17:47.310 --> 17:48.470
I'll save all the delicious food

17:48.490 --> 17:49.250
for you in the future.

17:49.350 --> 17:50.450
I'll eat the yucky ones.

17:50.470 --> 17:52.020
You'll save me all the delicious food.

17:52.080 --> 17:53.020
You heard that?

17:54.940 --> 17:55.860
You even made it nod?

17:55.880 --> 17:56.650
Yes.

17:56.990 --> 17:58.150
It's all recorded.

18:00.180 --> 18:00.930
Here.

18:15.360 --> 18:16.240
Thank you.

18:18.200 --> 18:19.840
You... You still remember?

18:20.980 --> 18:22.070
I'm used to it.

18:27.410 --> 18:28.430
Some things

18:31.830 --> 18:33.350
can never be forgotten.

19:02.210 --> 19:07.420
[Dormitory No.8]

19:06.530 --> 19:07.880
Do you remember that

19:08.080 --> 19:09.780
back then, a girl

19:09.850 --> 19:11.210
confessed her feelings to me here at the dorm entrance?

19:18.320 --> 19:19.110
Who was she?

19:19.780 --> 19:20.630
Playing dumb?

19:24.060 --> 19:24.510
Auntie.

19:25.190 --> 19:27.040
Please contact my classmate in Room 305.

19:27.430 --> 19:28.350
She has something to return to me,

19:28.370 --> 19:29.450
but I can't reach her.

19:29.750 --> 19:30.590
Return your stuff?

19:31.870 --> 19:33.510
I've seen too many tricks

19:33.530 --> 19:34.760
from boys like you.

19:34.930 --> 19:36.700
You're getting more and more unruly.

19:36.820 --> 19:37.890
Read carefully.

19:38.270 --> 19:39.450
The girls' dormitory is locked

19:39.510 --> 19:40.910
after 11:30 pm.

19:40.990 --> 19:41.800
If anyone goes out after that,

19:41.870 --> 19:43.380
her moral points will be deducted.

19:43.750 --> 19:44.590
I know.

19:46.550 --> 19:47.390
If you don't call her for me,

19:47.430 --> 19:48.310
I'll do it myself.

19:48.330 --> 19:49.070
No shouting.

19:51.870 --> 19:53.130
-Lu Yan.
-Don't.

19:53.540 --> 19:54.940
-Stop screaming.
-Lu Yan.

19:54.280 --> 19:57.160
[Dormitory No.8]

19:55.110 --> 19:55.550
Lu Yan!

19:55.590 --> 19:56.230
Stop screaming!

19:56.470 --> 19:56.990
Lu Yan!

19:56.990 --> 19:57.750
Stop it!

19:57.790 --> 19:58.350
Alright, alright.

19:58.400 --> 19:59.150
Wait here.

19:59.190 --> 19:59.790
Thank you, Auntie.

20:04.110 --> 20:07.460
[Dormitory No.8]

20:08.490 --> 20:09.000
Alright.

20:09.030 --> 20:10.030
You can talk here.

20:10.290 --> 20:11.410
Only ten minutes.

20:11.710 --> 20:12.640
Okay, you guys talk.

20:29.660 --> 20:30.620
Give me the book.

20:30.920 --> 20:31.850
What book?

20:31.990 --> 20:33.160
The one in your hand.

20:33.580 --> 20:34.510
This one?

20:45.110 --> 20:46.470
Where did that thing in my book go?

20:49.030 --> 20:50.500
You mean

20:50.630 --> 20:51.670
this photo?

20:55.110 --> 20:56.590
If I remember it right, this photo

20:56.590 --> 20:58.350
was a group photo.

20:58.470 --> 20:59.310
Why did you

20:59.310 --> 21:00.030
crop me out,

21:00.070 --> 21:01.050
enlarge it,

21:01.080 --> 21:02.200
and put it in your book?

21:04.390 --> 21:05.430
Give me back the photo.

21:06.870 --> 21:09.010
You don't look like a pervert.

21:09.830 --> 21:11.020
Do you like me?

21:14.430 --> 21:15.540
Give me back the photo.

21:20.550 --> 21:21.130
Alright.

21:21.630 --> 21:22.620
If you don't tell me,

21:22.830 --> 21:23.710
I'll keep the photo.

21:26.310 --> 21:27.510
That's my stuff.

21:31.600 --> 21:32.960
Jiang Chengyi is really something.

21:32.990 --> 21:34.230
He looks like a romantic lead.

21:34.480 --> 21:35.270
Others might think

21:35.270 --> 21:36.390
he's going to elope with Yan.

21:37.310 --> 21:38.320
It's just we can't hear

21:38.350 --> 21:39.390
what they're saying.

21:39.730 --> 21:40.310
It's okay.

21:40.330 --> 21:40.910
When Yan comes back,

21:40.910 --> 21:41.990
we can interrogate her and make her spill.

21:44.210 --> 21:45.430
You like me.

21:45.460 --> 21:46.230
If you like me,

21:46.230 --> 21:47.430
why don't you ask me to be your girlfriend?

21:56.470 --> 21:57.510
I guess it's because

21:59.410 --> 22:00.890
you want to be a policeman.

22:02.390 --> 22:03.550
I guess

22:03.590 --> 22:05.650
you want to apply for a postgraduate degree at the University of Public Security.

22:05.750 --> 22:06.960
You're worried that

22:06.990 --> 22:08.350
we won't be able to stay together for long.

22:08.550 --> 22:09.290
Right?

22:09.520 --> 22:12.180
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

22:12.940 --> 22:15.970
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

22:13.750 --> 22:14.390
You're right.

22:15.690 --> 22:17.200
There's no way I can stay here for you,

22:17.120 --> 22:19.510
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

22:18.010 --> 22:19.410
and I can't take you with me.

22:19.920 --> 22:21.100
So we...

22:20.130 --> 22:23.090
♫I kiss your face secretly♫

22:22.610 --> 22:23.510
I'll not waste your time.

22:24.460 --> 22:27.210
♫I want to weave a beautiful dream for you♫

22:28.040 --> 22:30.330
♫What we lack is not just time♫

22:28.210 --> 22:29.140
Jiang Chengyi.

22:29.760 --> 22:31.340
I haven't finished yet.

22:32.240 --> 22:34.670
♫Losing sight of the world and our default end point♫

22:35.540 --> 22:37.910
♫As we write every page of our love by hand♫

22:36.460 --> 22:37.520
Who knows

22:37.550 --> 22:39.930
