22:38.610 --> 22:41.450
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

22:42.570 --> 22:45.140
♫Romance only exists with you♫

22:43.320 --> 22:44.630
Since we're in love now,

22:44.630 --> 22:46.290
why can't we be together?

22:46.290 --> 22:48.180
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

22:46.580 --> 22:47.920
Even if it's only for a year,

22:48.070 --> 22:49.220
or three months,

22:49.090 --> 22:52.390
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

22:49.390 --> 22:50.610
or however long.

22:53.240 --> 22:54.770
As long as we cherish it,

22:53.560 --> 22:56.090
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

22:54.810 --> 22:56.120
we won't leave any regrets.

22:56.770 --> 22:58.340
Have you heard that saying?

22:57.180 --> 22:59.800
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

22:58.490 --> 23:00.720
Only dreams and love cannot be let down.

23:00.590 --> 23:02.820
♫Endless loving and longing♫

23:01.870 --> 23:02.910
We both lived up

23:02.930 --> 23:03.890
to our dreams.

23:04.030 --> 23:11.110
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

23:04.780 --> 23:05.590
Well,

23:07.160 --> 23:08.200
let's not

23:08.230 --> 23:09.200
let down our love too, okay?

23:19.980 --> 23:20.760
Go back.

23:21.210 --> 23:21.940
Don't catch a cold.

23:24.160 --> 23:26.860
♫Holding hands while heading to the best outcome♫

23:27.780 --> 23:30.750
♫Learning the beauty of waiting♫

23:31.890 --> 23:34.320
♫You know me best, I don't need to speak a word♫

23:35.280 --> 23:37.870
♫A special thing only you know♫

23:39.500 --> 23:42.170
♫I want to weave a beautiful dream for you♫

23:39.820 --> 23:41.250
Yan, come on!

23:42.550 --> 23:44.310
Do you want to be my boyfriend?

23:42.870 --> 23:45.530
♫I'll engrave every fluttering moment♫

23:45.340 --> 23:46.100
What do you say?

23:46.260 --> 23:47.100
Do you want to be my boyfriend?

23:46.830 --> 23:49.340
♫I kiss your forehead, as starlight watches us grow old together♫

23:49.630 --> 23:50.970
We're outside now.

23:50.240 --> 23:52.730
♫I want to hear you say you don't regret♫

23:51.370 --> 23:53.210
Do you want to be my boyfriend or not?

23:53.250 --> 23:54.540
Come down first.

23:53.400 --> 23:56.070
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

23:57.450 --> 23:59.890
♫Romance only exists with you♫

24:00.000 --> 24:01.460
If you're willing,

24:00.960 --> 24:02.790
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

24:01.480 --> 24:02.490
wait for me at the finish line

24:02.520 --> 24:04.050
