24:03.810 --> 24:07.540
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

24:04.310 --> 24:05.180
on the school sports day.

24:08.380 --> 24:11.070
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

24:12.100 --> 24:14.690
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

24:15.540 --> 24:17.760
♫Endless loving and longing♫

24:18.980 --> 24:26.060
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

24:52.360 --> 24:53.680
Now that we're revisiting this place full of memories,

24:54.790 --> 24:56.450
do you have anything you want to say to me?

25:00.030 --> 25:01.220
