27:27.560 --> 27:32.060
♫You don't exist♫

27:33.060 --> 27:38.330
♫Our love still exists♫

27:40.130 --> 27:45.080
♫I want to hear you telling the truth♫

27:45.230 --> 27:46.790
Will you come to the hospital tomorrow

27:46.490 --> 27:49.190
♫You know me best♫

27:48.030 --> 27:49.110
to see Uncle?

27:50.480 --> 27:52.050
♫With just one word♫

27:52.390 --> 27:54.620
I'll go straight to the airport.

27:53.320 --> 28:00.940
♫We'll overcome despair♫

27:55.350 --> 27:56.600
I've told them today.

28:04.530 --> 28:06.000
Have a safe trip.

28:11.390 --> 28:12.250
Lu Yan.

28:17.550 --> 28:18.790
My flight is at nine tomorrow.

28:19.840 --> 28:20.460
I'll go now.

28:52.830 --> 28:54.560
What do you have to tell me?

28:55.230 --> 28:57.040
Why did you suddenly break up with me back then?

28:58.310 --> 28:59.270
Yan.

29:00.150 --> 29:01.190
Help me!

29:01.210 --> 29:02.360
Help me!

29:09.730 --> 29:12.010
Aren't you my best friend?

29:13.010 --> 29:14.260
Why don't you

29:14.630 --> 29:17.070
give me any chance?

29:17.790 --> 29:20.350
Why do you have to push me to the edge?

29:21.150 --> 29:22.630
Why?

29:37.850 --> 29:38.680
What's up?

29:39.200 --> 29:40.630
There's a patient with gastric bleeding at the ER.

29:41.270 --> 29:42.150
Okay, I'll be right there.

31:09.420 --> 31:10.220
[Operating Area]

31:25.230 --> 31:25.920
Lu Yan

31:27.750 --> 31:30.490
♫To meet you in this big world♫

31:29.750 --> 31:31.070
My flight is at nine tomorrow.

31:30.860 --> 31:33.300
♫I'm excited like a child♫

31:33.140 --> 31:34.660
Should I go see him off?

31:34.430 --> 31:40.080
♫As we carve our future♫

31:41.380 --> 31:44.020
♫You're like the day that breaks up the night♫

31:45.100 --> 31:47.460
