31:54.110 --> 31:56.010
♫I don't understand♫

31:57.230 --> 31:58.570
♫How can I understand?♫

32:01.140 --> 32:05.390
♫You don't exist♫

32:07.210 --> 32:12.590
♫Our love still exists♫

32:13.800 --> 32:19.770
♫It's impossible to be apart♫

32:22.550 --> 32:25.950
♫Living in this world as if nothing happened♫

32:27.370 --> 32:29.050
♫No matter how the scenery changes♫

32:30.070 --> 32:35.570
♫The dust doesn't stay♫

32:37.210 --> 32:39.800
♫Empty double bed♫

32:41.040 --> 32:43.340
♫Our intertwined breaths were too intense♫

32:44.200 --> 32:45.110
Hello.

32:44.400 --> 32:48.450
♫I can't let it go♫

32:45.360 --> 32:46.220
I want to know

32:46.270 --> 32:48.560
if the flight to Jinzhou has taken off yet.

32:48.590 --> 32:49.370
Hello, madam.

32:49.160 --> 32:51.050
♫It's snowing heavily♫

32:49.390 --> 32:50.760
The flight has already boarded

32:50.790 --> 32:51.810
and is ready to take off.

32:52.680 --> 32:53.600
Thank you.

32:52.840 --> 32:55.440
♫Bury the dream♫

32:56.330 --> 33:01.070
♫And wait till you come back♫

33:03.130 --> 33:08.130
♫Our love still exists♫

33:09.830 --> 33:15.090
♫I want to hear you telling the truth♫

33:16.400 --> 33:18.930
♫You know me best♫

33:19.840 --> 33:23.080
♫If we just struggled a bit♫

33:23.990 --> 33:31.420
♫We'll overcome despair♫

33:32.980 --> 33:35.090
♫I try our best to make you stay♫

33:33.950 --> 33:35.750
I've completed all the procedures.

33:36.080 --> 33:37.840
I'm leaving the campus today.

33:36.210 --> 33:43.470
♫It's not that I can't stand being alone♫

33:38.350 --> 33:40.320
But I'm still at the school gate.

33:40.380 --> 33:41.820
I'll wait for you for the last three minutes.

33:42.070 --> 33:43.160
Consider it

33:43.190 --> 33:44.740
as our last chance.

33:46.790 --> 33:48.830
♫The person you can never forget♫

33:50.020 --> 33:55.730
♫Whom you love the most hurts the most♫

33:57.260 --> 34:02.640
♫Our love still exists♫

34:03.280 --> 34:05.500
[Ninghai University]

34:03.930 --> 34:09.639
♫It's impossible to be apart♫

34:11.110 --> 34:12.880
♫Forgive me for being silly♫

34:13.840 --> 34:17.280
♫I still look forward to the truth♫

34:18.070 --> 34:23.239
♫It tests my tenacity♫

34:23.940 --> 34:29.540
♫Our love still exists♫

34:30.880 --> 34:36.340
♫I want to hear you telling the truth♫

34:32.050 --> 34:32.840
[Ninghai University]

34:36.469 --> 34:37.230
Lu Yan.

34:37.610 --> 34:40.130
♫You know me best♫

34:40.940 --> 34:43.210
♫If we just struggled a bit♫

34:44.380 --> 34:52.350
♫We'll overcome despair♫

34:47.409 --> 34:48.230
What are you looking at?

34:54.650 --> 34:55.480
I...

34:55.500 --> 34:57.290
I just checked with a ground attendant,

34:58.080 --> 34:59.870
and she said your plane has taken off.

35:01.000 --> 35:01.630
Yes.

35:02.450 --> 35:03.450
I'm not leaving anymore.

35:05.250 --> 35:06.530
Why aren't you leaving?

35:10.280 --> 35:11.750
Eight years ago, I waited for you, but you didn't show up.

35:11.950 --> 35:13.560
This time, I thought I'd give it a try

35:14.120 --> 35:15.270
and see if you'd come.

35:18.070 --> 35:18.870
Why did you...

35:22.630 --> 35:23.740
Wait for me?

35:26.360 --> 35:27.770
Actually, I don't know either.

35:31.950 --> 35:33.150
What do you mean by not leaving?

35:34.960 --> 35:35.960
I got transferred back,

35:36.990 --> 35:38.140
back to Ninghai.

35:37.920 --> 35:39.270
♫As the city flickers♫

35:38.270 --> 35:39.190
I don't need to go back anymore.

35:40.430 --> 35:43.400
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

35:40.840 --> 35:41.460
It...

35:42.210 --> 35:42.970
It happened just now?

35:44.150 --> 35:45.130
Yes, just now.

35:44.600 --> 35:45.970
♫And you, who love to smile♫

35:46.990 --> 35:49.450
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

35:50.110 --> 35:51.850
You should have called me.

35:50.470 --> 35:52.820
♫The humor of time♫

35:51.870 --> 35:53.020
You didn't have to come all the way here.

35:53.100 --> 35:54.410
It was a waste of time, wasn't it?

35:54.000 --> 35:56.750
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

35:55.440 --> 35:57.400
I don't have your number.

35:57.680 --> 35:59.310
Didn't I write it down for you

35:57.820 --> 36:03.580
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

35:59.640 --> 36:00.770
last time?

36:03.020 --> 36:04.510
