36:04.960 --> 36:06.580
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

36:07.690 --> 36:10.550
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

36:10.200 --> 36:10.730
Come on.

36:11.840 --> 36:13.270
♫The stubborn me♫

36:12.400 --> 36:13.390
