36:14.360 --> 36:17.200
♫I always think of the far future♫

36:17.980 --> 36:20.050
♫I walk willfully♫

36:21.430 --> 36:24.350
♫Like a star revolving around♫

36:21.720 --> 36:26.700
[Lu Yan]

36:24.990 --> 36:26.300
♫I turn around♫

36:27.460 --> 36:30.960
♫But you're not behind me♫

36:29.420 --> 36:30.980
