36:32.630 --> 36:34.220
♫Losing you♫

36:33.770 --> 36:35.480
[Jiang Chengyi]

36:35.030 --> 36:37.210
♫It's so unreal♫

36:38.400 --> 36:39.830
♫I hurt my love♫

36:40.400 --> 36:41.490
♫But still hope to♫

36:41.570 --> 36:43.040
[Lu Yan]

36:42.240 --> 36:44.940
♫Start anew♫

36:46.130 --> 36:48.150
♫There’s a certain kind of squander♫

36:48.020 --> 36:49.060
The

36:49.090 --> 36:51.220
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

36:49.830 --> 36:51.280
transfer orders of the Public Security Bureau

36:51.300 --> 36:52.080
are usually issued

36:52.320 --> 36:53.440
