36:52.780 --> 36:54.750
♫When you're not here♫

36:54.710 --> 36:56.240
I don't know about that.

36:55.550 --> 36:58.850
♫Life becomes aimless♫

36:56.290 --> 36:57.970
I'm just following the arrangement.

36:59.720 --> 37:01.400
♫I miss you♫

37:00.060 --> 37:00.930
Liar.

37:01.960 --> 37:02.890
Why should I lie to you?

37:02.480 --> 37:04.620
♫It's so real♫

37:03.200 --> 37:04.140
You think

37:04.490 --> 37:05.800
